  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Open label study of sorafenib
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Open label study using oral sorafenib 800 mg daily in any stage III-IV BAC lung cancer and
      Stage III-IV adenocarcinoma of the lung in nonsmokers (less than &lt; 100 cigarettes lifetime).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
